Actions on Cultural Objects

 

To view actions available on the Cultural Object select Action option. A list with all actions will be displayed.

The actions depend on the Cultural Object status. The following Cultural Objects statuses are possible:

  • For Import - The Cultural Object is not imported from the CMS system yet. In this status the Cultural Object can be viewed only in Search in External system screen. The header of the object is not clickable and only basic information is visible in the header in order the Cultural Object to be identified and imported. In this state the Cultural Object can only be imported in CS, no other operations are available.
  • Current - Current version of the Cultural Object. Most of the actions that are for managing the Cultural Object are available in that state
  • Obsolete - Obsolete status of the Cultural Object. This is inactive status, and the Cultural Object data cannot be updates
